casebody.head_matter:
Cameron THOMAS, Petitioner
v.
NEVADA
No. 19-5967
Supreme Court of the United States.
November 18, 2019
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until December 9, 2019, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
